label: clads2-1
description: Grid computation for the full ClaDS2 model. Part of verification. No survivorship bias correction.
ppl:
var tree = phyjs.bisse_32
	var particles = 5000
	var MAX_LAMBDA = 5
	var MAX_DIV = 5
	var MIN_LAMBDA = 0.00001
	var PANDA = false
var model = function()
{
	var sigma = 0.15
	var alpha = 0.4
	var epsilon = 0.015
	var lambda = 0.03
	var rho = 1
	
	if (sigma == 0.000001 && alpha != 1.0) return NaN
	var ret = simClaDS2( tree, lambda, alpha, sigma, epsilon, rho )
	return ret
}
var dist = Infer({method: 'SMC', particles: particles, model: model})
dist.normalizationConstant
